76561198138131789,Not Recommended,291010,15782746,"Posted: 10 May, 2015",all,nta1996,"The Hat Man: Shadow Ward is a survival horror game where you play as a parent trying to find your daughter in an insane asylum. Along the way, you collect items, pages from your daughter's journal, and avoid the Hat Man. At first, I was impressed with the graphics, sound, and voice overs. Once the game began however, my enthusiasm was drained to find out it was just another Slender style game. I was disappointed by this because the idea and concept of this game was so great. It could have become a great adventure, survival horror game, but by modeling the game play of a Slender game, it just becomes a ""spin off"" of Slender. I wouldn't abandon the concept at all, but instead work towards making a bigger game with the concept. As much as I like the concept however, I just can't recommend this game I'm afraid."
